# RZGB Project — Cursor Rules
# Full context is in .ai-context.md — read it first before making any changes.

## Two Brands, One Codebase
- **Zaproc** (zaproc.co.uk) — SaaS procurement platform for manufacturing
- **RZ Global Solutions** (rzglobalsolutions.co.uk) — bespoke component supply broker
- Domain detected at runtime in `src/lib/portalConfig.js` via `window.location.hostname`

## Stack
- React 18 + Vite (JSX only — no TypeScript)
- Tailwind CSS (no CSS modules, no inline styles)
- Radix UI + shadcn components in `src/components/ui/`
- Lucide React for icons
- Framer Motion for animations
- Supabase for auth + database (RLS enabled, workspace_id scoped)
- React Router v6

## Import Alias
- `@/` = `src/` — always use this, never relative `../../`

## Key Files
- `src/lib/portalConfig.js` — domain routing logic (isRZGBDomain, isLandingDomain, getPortalUrl)
- `src/App.jsx` — all routes and providers
- `src/contexts/AuthContext.jsx` — useAuth() hook
- `src/pages/HomeOrRedirect.jsx` — picks landing page by domain
- `src/pages/RZGBLandingPage.jsx` — rzglobalsolutions.co.uk landing
- `src/pages/LandingPage.jsx` — zaproc.co.uk landing
- `src/components/DomainGuard.jsx` — redirects non-root paths on landing domains
- `public/.htaccess` — SPA routing on Hostinger Apache (do not delete)

## Auth Roles
super_admin > customer_admin > client > supplier
All DB queries must be scoped by workspace_id.

## Styling
- Light theme default, dark via ThemeContext toggle
- RZGB: slate + orange-500 accent, glassmorphism (backdrop-blur, bg-white/10, border-white/20)
- Zaproc: sky blue + slate, clean minimal
- Fonts: Inter (headings) + DM Sans (body) — loaded in index.html

## Git / Deploy
- `main` is protected — PRs only, Build + Lint checks must pass
- Hostinger auto-deploys both sites from `main`
- `.env` is gitignored — set VITE_SUPABASE_URL + VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY in Hostinger dashboard

## Do Not
- No TypeScript, no CSS files, no styled-components
- No react-icons (use lucide-react)
- No window.location.href for internal nav (use React Router)
- No new Supabase clients (use src/lib/supabase.js or supabaseAdmin.js)
- No console.log in production code
- Never commit .env or service role keys

